query:
-- Get total California stats
SELECT 
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.id) as total_agencies,
    COUNT(p.id) as total_protocols
FROM counties c
LEFT JOIN protocolChunks p ON c.id = p.countyId
WHERE c.state = 'California';
